          "valueSource": "expr",
          "expression": "tag(\r\nsplit({RootInstanceName},\u0027_\u0027)[len(split({RootInstanceName},\u0027_\u0027))-2,0]\r\n+\u0027/Electrical/Meter/\u0027+{meterName}+\u0027/Digital Inputs/DI_S5\u0027\r\n)",
